fields.value: Replication Data for: Improving Ecological Inference by Predicting Individual Ethnicity from Voter Registration Records

dsDescriptionValue.value: Replication files for Imai & Khanna (2016) "Improving Ecological Inference by Predicting Individual Ethnicity from Voter Registration Records", including replication data, codebook, and R scripts to produce all analyses in the paper. Only academic use permitted.
